          <p className="text-zinc-400 mb-4 leading-relaxed">Being ahead of an algorithm change is one of the most powerful competitive advantages in social media. While everyone else is scrambling to figure out why their reach dropped, you have already pivoted your content strategy and are capturing the traffic they lost. This is not about gaming the system. It is about understanding the rules of the game and playing intelligently.</p>
